## Climbing

---


[Entity Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_condition_types/climbing)

Checks whether the entity is currently climbing.

Type ID: `origins:climbing`

---

### Examples
```json
"condition": {
    "type": "origins:climbing"
}
```
